"smart_blocks:_007.Books/Wild at Heart.md#Wild at Heart#This is where many people feel abandoned or betrayed by God. They thought that becoming a Christian would somehow end their troubles, or at least reduce them considerably. No one ever told them they were being moved to the front lines, and they seem genuinely shocked at the fact that they’ve been shot at. (Page 85)#{1}": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.03955165,0.01997772,0.00028285,0.03053862,0.01217135,-0.00315797,0.0368759,0.0506616,0.01476158,-0.04747032,0.01193812,-0.01063397,0.05108616,-0.02530267,-0.01621744,0.02451357,-0.02628787,0.009672,-0.11551072,0.06516847,-0.03181728,0.02685625,0.06503621,-0.08430739,0.04263202,-0.00393538,-0.02946822,-0.05592236,-0.07645382,-0.1316155,-0.01636062,-0.01594089,0.02280637,0.01198972,0.02816136,0.00089577,-0.04415557,0.03435503,-0.00815575,0.07980978,0.08057277,0.06426562,-0.00200633,-0.01025859,0.03239274,-0.00645618,-0.04529043,-0.04445536,0.07522479,-0.01342291,-0.10516473,0.02992208,-0.01810669,0.03293946,0.01482766,-0.02036476,0.10679887,0.01282881,0.01729638,0.01997652,0.08935161,0.00249852,-0.10891493,0.04933623,0.0133202,0.04165521,-0.03692828,0.0119983,0.0267373,0.0445141,-0.04674531,0.02232828,-0.01171883,0.03082455,0.02293197,-0.00517445,-0.01088412,-0.0394255,0.0026649,0.0247618,0.00665722,-0.0357371,-0.03180063,-0.0341862,-0.08088217,-0.04880321,0.08758043,-0.05606128,0.03210149,0.02013136,0.04517249,0.04028356,0.05202598,0.0617566,-0.02422978,-0.0170399,0.0350069,0.032277,-0.08934904,0.14384823,-0.03924197,0.04577952,-0.02575325,0.00009181,0.07326075,-0.00186241,0.01409785,-0.0287975,-0.01163934,-0.01704019,0.09289221,-0.01732618,0.00667008,-0.08611006,0.08942915,-0.03670574,0.05499869,0.00745382,-0.02665325,0.02456917,-0.04713459,-0.0155464,0.06826232,-0.01190835,-0.00260729,-0.11493333,-0.01736098,0.06790575,0.07901275,-0.0319817,-0.00173984,-0.02436908,-0.0537428,-0.06417721,0.01119677,0.02460898,0.01694063,0.03330995,0.